"use strict";(self.webpackChunkchasingcloudcareers=self.webpackChunkchasingcloudcareers||[]).push([[5437],{505:e=>{e.exports=JSON.parse('{"archive":{"blogPosts":[{"id":"welcome-to-chasing-cloud-careers","metadata":{"permalink":"/chasingcloudcareers-site/blog/welcome-to-chasing-cloud-careers","editUrl":"https://github.com/mrcloudchase/chasingcloudcareers-site/tree/main/blog/2025-01-15-welcome-to-chasing-cloud-careers/index.md","source":"@site/blog/2025-01-15-welcome-to-chasing-cloud-careers/index.md","title":"Welcome to Chasing Cloud Careers - Your Free Path to Engineering Success","description":"We\'re thrilled to welcome you to Chasing Cloud Careers - a completely free, community-driven platform designed to help you break into and advance in engineering careers. Whether you\'re making your first career transition or looking to level up your existing skills, we\'re here to guide you every step of the way.","date":"2025-01-15T00:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":false,"label":"Career Change","permalink":"/chasingcloudcareers-site/blog/tags/career-change","description":"Tips and guidance for transitioning into engineering careers"},{"inline":false,"label":"Learning Paths","permalink":"/chasingcloudcareers-site/blog/tags/learning-paths","description":"Structured guides for different engineering disciplines"},{"inline":false,"label":"Getting Started","permalink":"/chasingcloudcareers-site/blog/tags/getting-started","description":"Beginner-friendly content for new learners"},{"inline":false,"label":"Community","permalink":"/chasingcloudcareers-site/blog/tags/community","description":"Community updates, events, and collaboration"},{"inline":false,"label":"Free Resources","permalink":"/chasingcloudcareers-site/blog/tags/free-resources","description":"Curated free learning materials and tools"}],"readingTime":5.19,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"Chase Dovey","title":"Cloud Engineering Advocate & Community Builder","url":"https://github.com/mrcloudchase","page":{"permalink":"/chasingcloudcareers-site/blog/authors/chasedovey"},"socials":{"github":"https://github.com/mrcloudchase","linkedin":"https://www.linkedin.com/in/chasedovey/","x":"https://x.com/mrcloudchase"},"imageURL":"https://github.com/mrcloudchase.png","key":"chasedovey"},{"name":"Emma Schwarz","title":"Engineering Career Mentor & Content Creator","url":"https://linkedin.com/in/emmaschwarz","page":{"permalink":"/chasingcloudcareers-site/blog/authors/emmaschwarz"},"socials":{"linkedin":"https://www.linkedin.com/in/emmaschwarz/","github":"https://github.com/emmaschwarz","x":"https://x.com/emmaschwarz"},"imageURL":"https://github.com/emmaschwarz.png","key":"emmaschwarz"}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"welcome-to-chasing-cloud-careers","title":"Welcome to Chasing Cloud Careers - Your Free Path to Engineering Success","authors":["chasedovey","emmaschwarz"],"tags":["career-change","learning-paths","getting-started","community","free-resources"],"image":"./welcome-hero.png"},"unlisted":false},"content":"We\'re thrilled to welcome you to **Chasing Cloud Careers** - a completely free, community-driven platform designed to help you break into and advance in engineering careers. Whether you\'re making your first career transition or looking to level up your existing skills, we\'re here to guide you every step of the way.\\n\\n![Welcome to Chasing Cloud Careers](./welcome-hero.png)\\n\\n\x3c!-- truncate --\x3e\\n\\n## Our Story\\n\\nChasing Cloud Careers was born from a simple belief: **everyone deserves access to high-quality engineering education, regardless of their financial situation**. We\'ve curated the best free resources from across the internet, organized them into structured learning paths, and built a supportive community around shared learning and growth.\\n\\nThis isn\'t about selling you courses or certifications. This is about empowering you with the knowledge, skills, and confidence to chase your engineering dreams.\\n\\n## Six Comprehensive Learning Paths\\n\\nWe\'ve designed six distinct learning paths, each tailored to different engineering disciplines and career goals:\\n\\n### Support Engineering\\nPerfect for those who love problem-solving and helping others. Learn technical troubleshooting, customer success principles, and the art of turning frustrated users into happy customers. This path is ideal for career changers who want to enter tech with strong communication skills.\\n\\n**What you\'ll master:**\\n- Technical troubleshooting methodologies\\n- Customer communication and empathy\\n- Product knowledge and documentation\\n- Escalation management and team collaboration\\n\\n### Linux Engineering\\nDive deep into the backbone of modern infrastructure. Master command-line interfaces, system administration, and the skills that power everything from web servers to cloud platforms. Linux knowledge is foundational for almost every other engineering discipline.\\n\\n**What you\'ll master:**\\n- Command line proficiency and shell scripting\\n- System administration and user management\\n- Network configuration and security\\n- Server management and performance optimization\\n\\n### Cloud Engineering\\nLearn to build, deploy, and manage applications in the cloud. Explore AWS, Azure, and Google Cloud Platform while mastering infrastructure as code, containerization, and cloud-native architectures. This is where the future of infrastructure is heading.\\n\\n**What you\'ll master:**\\n- Multi-cloud platform expertise (AWS, Azure, GCP)\\n- Infrastructure as Code with Terraform and CloudFormation\\n- Containerization with Docker and Kubernetes\\n- Cloud security and cost optimization\\n\\n### DevOps Engineering\\nBridge the gap between development and operations. Learn to automate deployments, manage CI/CD pipelines, and create the systems that allow software teams to ship faster and more reliably. DevOps engineers are in high demand across all industries.\\n\\n**What you\'ll master:**\\n- CI/CD pipeline design and implementation\\n- Container orchestration and microservices\\n- Monitoring, logging, and observability\\n- Infrastructure automation and configuration management\\n\\n### AI Engineering\\nStep into the future of technology. Learn to build, deploy, and maintain AI systems in production. This isn\'t just about training models - it\'s about creating the infrastructure and processes that make AI applications reliable and scalable.\\n\\n**What you\'ll master:**\\n- MLOps and model lifecycle management\\n- AI infrastructure and deployment strategies\\n- Model monitoring and performance optimization\\n- Ethical AI practices and governance\\n\\n### Research Engineering\\nFor those who want to push the boundaries of what\'s possible. Learn to bridge cutting-edge research with practical implementation, working at the intersection of academia and industry. Partner with our **AJ (Average Joes) Labs** community for real-world research projects.\\n\\n**What you\'ll master:**\\n- Research methodology and experimental design\\n- Academic paper implementation and analysis\\n- Prototype development and proof-of-concept creation\\n- Collaboration between research and engineering teams\\n\\n## Built by the Community, For the Community\\n\\nWhat makes Chasing Cloud Careers special isn\'t just our content - it\'s our community. We believe that learning happens best when people support each other, share experiences, and grow together.\\n\\n### Why We Do This\\n\\n- **100% Free**: No hidden costs, no premium tiers, no paywalls\\n- **Community-Driven**: Built by engineers, for engineers\\n- **Practical Focus**: Real-world skills that employers actually want\\n- **Continuous Learning**: Updated regularly with industry trends and feedback\\n\\n### Join Our Growing Community\\n\\n- **Monthly Meetups**: Virtual sessions for each learning path\\n- **Study Groups**: Connect with learners at your level\\n- **Mentorship**: Get guidance from experienced professionals\\n- **Project Collaboration**: Work on real projects with other community members\\n- **Job Search Support**: Resume reviews, interview prep, and networking\\n\\n## Technologies We Cover\\n\\nDepending on your chosen learning path, you\'ll work with industry-standard tools and technologies:\\n\\n- **Cloud Platforms**: AWS, Azure, Google Cloud Platform\\n- **Containerization**: Docker, Kubernetes, container registries\\n- **Infrastructure**: Terraform, Ansible, CloudFormation\\n- **Programming**: Python, JavaScript, Go, Bash scripting\\n- **Databases**: PostgreSQL, MongoDB, Redis\\n- **Monitoring**: Prometheus, Grafana, ELK Stack\\n- **CI/CD**: Jenkins, GitHub Actions, GitLab CI\\n- **Version Control**: Git, GitHub, GitLab\\n\\n## Getting Started is Easy\\n\\n1. **Explore the Learning Paths**: Browse our six paths and choose the one that excites you most\\n2. **Start with Fundamentals**: Each path begins with foundational concepts\\n3. **Learn by Doing**: Follow along with hands-on projects and exercises\\n4. **Join the Community**: Connect with other learners and mentors\\n5. **Build Your Portfolio**: Create projects that showcase your new skills\\n6. **Land Your Dream Job**: Use our job search resources to make the transition\\n\\n## Success Stories\\n\\nOur community members have successfully transitioned into roles at:\\n- Major cloud providers (AWS, Microsoft, Google)\\n- Fast-growing startups and scale-ups\\n- Traditional enterprises embracing digital transformation\\n- Research institutions and innovation labs\\n- Consulting firms and agencies\\n\\n## What\'s Next?\\n\\nReady to start your engineering journey? Here\'s what we recommend:\\n\\n1. **Browse the Learning Paths**: Take some time to explore each path and see what resonates with you\\n2. **Join Our Community**: Connect with us on GitHub and follow our progress\\n3. **Start Learning**: Pick a path and begin with the \\"Getting Started\\" guide\\n4. **Share Your Journey**: Document your learning process and help others along the way\\n\\n## Connect With Us\\n\\nWe\'re always here to help and would love to hear from you:\\n\\n- **GitHub**: [mrcloudchase/chasingcloudcareers-site](https://github.com/mrcloudchase/chasingcloudcareers-site)\\n- **Community Discussions**: Join our GitHub Discussions for questions and collaboration\\n- **Feedback**: Help us improve by sharing your learning experience\\n\\n---\\n\\n## A Personal Note\\n\\nFrom all of us at Chasing Cloud Careers, thank you for being part of this journey. We started this project because we believe that with the right resources, community support, and determination, anyone can build a successful engineering career.\\n\\nYour success is our success. Every person who lands their dream job, solves their first production issue, or helps a colleague learn something new validates why we do this work.\\n\\n**Welcome to the community. Let\'s chase those cloud careers together!**\\n\\n---\\n\\n*Ready to begin? [Choose your learning path](/docs/intro) and start your transformation today.*"}]}}')}}]);